which we'll use in a moment inside of the style sheet,

00:03:12.635 --> 00:03:14.310
and then the two tech sections,

00:03:14.310 --> 00:03:17.930
the first one is now taking online applications,

00:03:17.930 --> 00:03:20.820
which we're going to wrap in a <p> element.

